{"tid":847843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以前係長輩教我地要有禮貌，到我地大個就係佢地最冇禮貌","createTime":"2018-10-04T12:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T01:56:52.000Z","uid":134683,"like":1457,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"c8a9ef40dc5e60f7567531948475a62c4bc2ba13","tid":847843,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"1.飲茶唔俾敲碗，唔準講太大聲因為會嘈到人，依家佢地就大大聲播片聽WhatsApp,叫佢細聲d佢仲鬧返你轉頭<br />\n2.細個教我地讓坐，我地大個睇住佢地掙位坐<br />\n3.細個教我地撞到人要道歉，依家佢地撞到人、個袋un到人、拉車轆到人、踩到人隻腳完全若無其事<br />\n4.細個教我地過馬路睇紅綠燈，依家佢地就亂咁過馬路<br />\n<br />\n其他仲有好多，挨扶手柱、周街剪指甲、撩鼻屎、睇報紙篤到前坐....<br />\n<br />\n我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3f8dff983f32a8f4030d3c730425312d9f6a38","tid":847843,"uid":134683,"like":241,"dislike":1,"score":240,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:02:34.000Z","msg":"搭車好地地瞓着<br />\n成日俾人d袋撞埋黎整醒左<br />\n冇一個覺得有唔妥冇一個會道歉<br />\n成日搭車俾呢d仆街整醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f86fc1580dfab97b56ad5fd1ae34a54a1511732","tid":847843,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17ae499aa4d113ab75799be96874bf604987b26","tid":847843,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2116f054d643f3fbb6bf65ed17c9c273b61e7ca","tid":847843,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57354244b41399ed9bcdb103f8e5b7a40154fd4e","tid":847843,"uid":39777,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:28:07.000Z","msg":"仲有排隊唔好打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/